		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Banshaku wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">What I meant is if there is any american game that are not compatible on the famicom?</div>
<br />Perhaps the games that require a non-standard controller (e.g. Miracle Piano) or a Four Score accessory (e.g. Smash TV) because those differ between the Famicom and the NES.

		

