	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Yes some games wouldn't work easily. The power pad and 4 player adapters work different. I can't remember if the famicom lightguns would work with a US game either. But without add-ons, they should work fine. Nintendo used the same circuit board types--just in different formats.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


